Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_int_info2

This register contains the invalid SRIO_OMSG_HDR_S associated with the OMSG_ERR interrupt. This register is only updated when the OMSG_ERR is initially detected. Once the interrupt is cleared then additional information can be captured.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
